          "url": "https://github.com/ACarloGitHub/Audiobook-Generator/releases/latest/download/qwen-tts-runtime-windows-x64.zip",
          "dest_dir": "resources/qwentts",
          "size_mb": 15,
          "note": "CUDA build produced by CI from unmodified upstream sources (GGML_BACKEND_DL=ON, CUDA archs 75;80;86;89;90). Bundles cudart/cublas/cublasLt and ggml-cpu.dll, so it falls back to CPU automatically on machines without an NVIDIA GPU. Vulkan variant and macOS/Linux builds still to do."
        }
